    <div class="container-fluid padding">
            <div class="row text-center">
            <!--Individuals-->
                <div class="col-12">
                    <h2>Services for Individuals</h2>
                    <hr class="serve">
                </div>


                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <h4>Retrenchment Training</h4>
                    <hr class="my-4">
                    <p>Ideal for individuals who are likely to experience
                            job loss. This course prepares participants to
                            manage the change process and structure their
                            terminal benefits to best meet their existing liabilities,
                            whilst focusing on creating income.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Personal Financial Induction</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Ideal for individuals who have just joined the
                                workforce and wish to get a head start in building
                                their net worth. This module ensures the participant
                                understand DEBT, CREDIT & INVESTMENT
                                early enough to avoid over indebtedness so as to
                                achieve their goals.</p>
                </div> 
                <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Personal Finance One on Ones</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Ideal for individuals who struggle to operate within
                                their budget. The individual is made aware of the
                                impact of their current spending plan on the
                                achievement of their long term goals.
                                Guidance is provided on appropriate investment
                                opportunities..</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Personal Finance</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Ideal for individuals who wish to regain control
                                over their money and start building personal
                                wealth. This module equips the participant to
                                develop effective debt management strategies,
                                create a savings potential and build a sustainable
                                diversified investment portfolio in line with their
                                risk tolerance.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4"></div>
                <div class="col-md-4"></div>
                <!--Members-->
                <div class="col-12"> 
                    <h2>Services for Members of Pension Funds</h2>
                    <hr class="serve">
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Member Education</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Aimed at members of pension funds. This course
                                provides members of retirement funds with the
                                requisite knowledge to fully participate in their
                                retirement preparation so as to achieve the retirement
                                they desire.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Trusteeship</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Suitable for newly appointed trustees, existing
                                trustees who need to improve their understanding
                                of the role of trustees and individuals who are
                                interested in trusteeship.
                                The course will equip individuals with detailed
                                knowledge of the retirement funds industry and its
                                functions and enable trustees to carry out their
                                duties with confidence.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Investment 103</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Appropriate for trustees who form part of the
                                investment committee or individuals who require a
                                deeper understanding of investment issues related
                                to the management of retirement funds. The
                                course will provide a more detailed analysis of
                                investment strategies and products. The sessions
                                will improve understanding of complex investment
                                issues and help participants to enhance the practical
                                application of their investment knowledge.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Pre-Retirement Training</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Appropriate for those 10 years and below to retirement.
                                The course equips individuals with the knowledge
                                to make informed decisions about their financial
                                habits and improve their standard of living after
                                retirement.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Fiduciary & Investment Combo</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Ideal for new and non-financial trustees. The objective
                                of the combined fiduciary and Investment
                                Combo is to introduce retirement industry concepts
                                at a pace understood by new trustees.</p>
                    </div>
                        <div class="col-md-4">
                        <h4>Fiduciary & Investment Combo</h4>
                        <hr class="my-4">
                        <p>Ideal for new and non-financial trustees. The objective
                                of the combined fiduciary and Investment
                                Combo is to introduce retirement industry concepts
                                at a pace understood by new trustees.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h4>Risk Management 101</h4>
                            <hr class="my-4">
                            <p>Suitable for trustees new to the concept of risk
                                    management. The objective of Risk Management
                                    101 is to provide the trustee with a basic understanding
                                    of risk and practical methods of its management.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h4>Risk Management 102</h4>
                            <hr class="my-4">
                            <p>Ideal for trustees with a basic understanding of Risk
                                    and those who sit on the Risk Management Committee
                                    of the Fund. The objective of the Risk Management
                                    102 Module is to develop a technical
                                    understanding of pension fund risk management to
                                    enable practical methods of managing risks.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h4>Near-Retirement Training</h4>
                            <hr class="my-4">
                            <p>Ideal for near retirees. The course will equip individuals
                                    with the knowledge to make informed decisions
                                    at retirement in order to maximise the value
                                    of their fund credit.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h4>Investment 101</h4>
                            <hr class="my-4">
                            <p>Aimed at trustees who are new to the retirement
                                    funds industry or need to improve their investment
                                    knowledge. The course provides an introduction to
                                    the basic investment concepts applied in the industry.
                                    The interactive sessions will lay the foundation
                                    for understanding more advanced investment
                                    topics.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4"></div>
                    <div class="col-md-4"></div>
                    <div class="col-12"> 
                            <h2>Services for Trustees of Pension Funds</h2>
                            <hr class="serve">
                        </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h4>Board Assessment</h4>
                            <hr class="my-4">
                            <p>A statutory requirement for every Retirement Fund
                                    Board. Annually the Board of Trustees of a Retirement
                                    Fund must engage an independent consultant
                                    to carry out the assessment of their performance as
                                    well as their processes and procedures.
                                    This assessment is a tool to enable the Board Members
                                    to track their progress and assess their development
                                    needs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h4>Investment 102</h4>
                            <hr class="my-4">
                            <p>Appropriate for trustees who have a basic understanding
                                    of investments but require a better grasp of
                                    investment issues. The course will provide individuals
                                    with a more advanced overview of investment
                                    topics related to the management of a retirement
                                    fund and enable trustees to participate more effectively
                                    on the Board when dealing with investment
                                    matters.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-4">
                            <h4>Fund Policies</h4>
                            <hr class="my-4">
                            <p>Appropriate for trustees who need to understand
                                    the issues involved in the development of regulatory
                                    policies. Trustees will learn about the factors that
                                    are important in the formulation of policies, regulatory
                                    requirements and the rationale behind the
                                    policies implemented. The course will equip trustees
                                    with the knowledge to participate more effectively
                                    in the discussion, development and review of
                                    fund governing documents.</p>
                    
                </div>

                </div>
